Frequently Asked Questions

How old is Reggie Jackson?

Reggie Jackson is 35 years old.

Where was Reggie Jackson born?

Reggie Jackson was born in Pordenone, Italy.

When was Reggie Jackson born?

Reggie Jackson was born on April 16, 1990.

How tall is Reggie Jackson?

Reggie Jackson is 6-2 (188 cm) tall.

How much does Reggie Jackson weigh?

Reggie Jackson weighs 208 lbs (94 kg).

Is Reggie Jackson in the Hall of Fame?

Reggie Jackson is not in the Hall of Fame.

When was Reggie Jackson drafted?

Reggie Jackson was drafted by Oklahoma City Thunder, 1st round (24th pick, 24th overall), 2011 NBA Draft.

What position does Reggie Jackson play?

Point Guard and Shooting Guard.

What is Reggie Jackson's net worth?

Reggie Jackson has made at least $118,381,140 playing professional basketball.

How much does Reggie Jackson make?

Reggie Jackson made $17,286,956 in 2020.

How many rings does Reggie Jackson have?

Reggie Jackson has won one championship.

What is Reggie Jackson's Instagram account?

Reggie Jackson is on Instagram at reggie_jackson.

What schools did Reggie Jackson attend?

Reggie Jackson attended Palmer in Colorado Springs, Colorado and Boston College.

What are Reggie Jackson's nicknames?

Mr. June, Big Government are nicknames for Reggie Jackson.
